Class SpeedyClock

java.lang.Object

      org.middleheaven.quantity.time.clocks.WrappedClock
          org.middleheaven.quantity.time.clocks.SpeedyClock

public class SpeedyClock
extends WrappedClock

A clock with variable cadence. SpeedyClock uses another clock as reference for the real time. This clock can be used to simulate faster or slower elapse of time
